<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrī śākābdē śararāmavahniśaśisaṁpūrnnē nabha
<lb n="2" break="no"/>syē ravāvaṣṭamyaṁ sitapakṣakē nṛharayēbhiṣṭarttasi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ddhyai prabhuḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> paṭānāyakaĒṣa paddatanayōmalāṁsu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>naṁdājvamā caṁdrarkkasuśōbhētāṁ guImahasēna
<lb n="5" break="no"/>patirddattavan <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1335 gunēṁṭi bha
<lb n="6" break="no"/>drapada śukla Aṣṭami bhanuparamunāṁḍu poṭnuri pa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>napadiminayani koḍuku paṭanāyaḍu guImahasē
<lb n="8" break="no"/>napati bhaṁḍārāna padmanidi Ipaḷavānāṁ tōṭaku nālu 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>gu maḍalu 4 ḍimila <unclear>śala</unclear>kṣētraṁ [pu 1 kini ku<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>capra<supplied reason="omitted">sā</supplied><unclear>damunnu</unclear>
<lb n="10"/>samapada maḍalu 10 vadi śrīnarasiṁhyanādaniki tanaku A
<lb n="11" break="no"/>bhīṣṭārttasiddhaganu da<unclear>ttaṁ</unclear> nityamunu ṟēpaṭi dupaAvasa
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ramaṁdu śrītulasivanamālalu 2 rātriṁṭi dupaAvasara
<lb n="13" break="no"/>maṁdu bhadasaragadadōḍa 1 Ivi peṭanā gōpaḷavanaṁ puvulu
<lb n="14" break="no"/>tōḍi Eluvupeṭi sarvvakalānaku bhumuAnnama
<lb n="15"/>bhasili vīraya Ānavala tamaya I mugurunnu sarvvakā
<lb n="16" break="no"/>lamunu I nirnnaṁcina puppulu peṭaṁgalā(ga)ru vīrikā kuḍajī
<lb n="17" break="no"/>tanuku I kṣētramu peṭināru I dharma śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrīśrīśrī
</p>

